d when upgrading to 4.2 .\n2. I've added the [foreman gem](https://github.com/ddollar/foreman). It is nicer and easier to have your environment variables in a `.env` file. I've also added `.env` to the .gitignore file. I can update the readme to reflect this in the Mailtrap section.\n3. I had a bit of trouble with other tests failing because they were trying to deliver the email. I've set `action_mailer.raise_delivery_errors` to `false`. Let me know if this is unacceptable, and I'll find another way.\n\n![Wiggle](http://i.imgur.com/4nQacF3.gif)\n\nBed time!\n", "created_at": "2015-03-10T00:31:48Z", "updated_at": "2015-03-10T11:01:00Z", "closed_at": "2015-03-10T10:24:34Z", "merged_at": "2015-03-10T10:24:34Z", "merge_commit_sha": "d3f273a90b5ceb79b7ab6345d296ed55b2126bd8", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/pulls/159/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/pulls/159/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/issues/159/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/statuses/e392f7b7d66b587c46b5911f95b7aef87e64ec94", "head": {"label": "marcgreenstock:send_email_when_added_to_team", "ref": "send_email_when_added_to_team", "sha": "e392f7b7d66b587c46b5911f95b7aef87e64ec94", "user": {"login": "marcgreenstock", "id": 287739, "avatar_url": "https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/287739?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/marcgreenstock", "html_url": "https://github.com/marcgreenstock", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marcgreenstock/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mar